bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.filter

Interface BFilter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BFilterImplem

    public interface BFilter
extends Cloneable
    This interface defines a SROutput filter. Such a filter aims at applying a set of constraints to retrieve BHits/BHSPs satisfying those constraints.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
